啱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:58:14.000Z","msg":"倒不如&hellip;<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fsanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721&d=m%2FvCTr80Ma3Q2SiS6jp77eQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=22a46f39\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/sanction-hong-kong-government-its-state-terrorism-activity-conducted-yuen-long-train-station-hong-kong-721</a>"},{"pid":"9ca170ecc9c6b09f6cf1afcda4d1ef7f59e7dbb4","tid":1415963,"uid":49994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c432b54986f30c2145f4a35730f863196d8cb551","tid":1415963,"uid":933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:00:20.000Z","msg":"屌 唔好比黑警五毛帶風向 持續嘅罷工 民意會反彈"},{"pid":"42abc3c4f7f569bf6036f00149ca7c0327ddf3db","tid":1415963,"uid":101824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:00:41.000Z","msg":"Agree<br />\n再集氣儲 下一次更長時間"},{"pid":"7a34631dcdf07368633c6d2168e5aa2ed0df7e1f","tid":1415963,"uid":186035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:01:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74cbe309e937dcf05869cdab3b75c6990345ae28","tid":1415963,"uid":100363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:02:48.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"632abd26a6c8c3e3a6865f66791b794f21ae85ee","tid":1415963,"uid":164190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ee06b7fa43713d57ddb707f2f1825429393bf41","tid":1415963,"uid":17232,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:27:43.000Z","msg":"今日已經有post提左大家<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">今朝記者會有一點詭異之處，好似冇人討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1412948\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1412948</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span><br />\n<br />\n林鄭高調表明<br />\n即日起警方每日四點鐘開記者會<br />\n<br />\n<ins>詭異之處：</ins><br />\n<br />\n1. 目前為止計劃嘅大罷工只有8月5日， 林鄭嘅安排好似預咗今個禮拜每日都大罷工<br />\n<br />\n2. 就算真係每日都有事故出現， 警方亦都可以即日通知安排記者會， 點解需要預先安排每日記者會？<br />\n<br />\n<ins>拆局</ins><br />\n<br />\n1. 林鄭想暗中煽動輿論令民眾喺條件未成熟之下發動每日罷工（ 佢知道民眾好容易受到煽動）<br />\n<br />\n2. 林鄭預計缺乏抖氣位（ 每日出現）嘅罷工 不能持續， 有利政府短時間內（10.1前）令抗爭運動無以為繼<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><ins>對策</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1. 8月5號大罷工成功</span></span></strong><br />\n一大原因係有成個禮拜嘅時間宣傳醞釀<br />\n最重要係畀打工仔安排<br />\n如果操之過急<br />\n打工仔好難安排變相就會冇人反應<br />\n罷工行動就會失敗（好似元朗恐襲之後嗰幾日）<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>2. 罷工要有永續性</strong></span></span><br />\n就要有位畀打工仔抖氣<br />\n可以慢慢升級、 加強密度<br />\n切忌一步登天<br />\n慢慢升級亦有利減少對市民嘅衝擊<br />\n一步步令更多市民支持<br />\n令到將來嘅罷工越嚟越大型<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">3. <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>林鄭而家嘅任務只有一個<br />\n就係10.1 前平息抗</strong></span></span><br />\n佢唔怕短時間內大型抗爭<br />\n只怕持續不衰嘅抗爭<br />\n抗爭持續不但會影響國慶<br />\n 更會影響建制派區議會選舉。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:07:18.000Z","msg":"Push be clamp be humble"},{"pid":"9e0f48bba9efb0e8946ef3a6fb64d53c33720d4c","tid":1415963,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:10:02.000Z","msg":"推 長期戰"},{"pid":"eb2f53d210da9e8b49f8c77b42d81ba9727c8dcc","tid":1415963,"uid":198258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:11:47.000Z","msg":"罷一日都咁難，點無限罷？"},{"pid":"323a4ade7f835af7ce6a352ee0fec75d453e0ab9","tid":1415963,"uid":52424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d0414801ee2aac918145407fd9883d9ac9594cc","tid":1415963,"uid":228656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:17:42.000Z","msg":"各位手足今日辛苦曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係時候比勇武休息一下 我地和你飛又出黎啦<br />\n搞掂晒今日唔該大家同我入嚟睇一睇8月9號可以點樣令到國際更加了解我哋嘅活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為真係好重要<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">特別係而家冇乜人知八月九和你飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n唔該大家幫手推一推<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">八月九號 機場見!</span></span><br />\n[人手置頂]搞掂好今日唔該即刻同我入嚟睇嚟緊8月9號可以做啲乜 我哋唔可以再輸 唔好再打飛機 好緊要!!!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416403\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416403</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b52b6bbaee037157adc9500b5003d1c162aa000a","tid":1415963,"uid":106870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:19:14.000Z","msg":"不要説：失民意，試著説：一齊贏翻民意<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dxawgS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dxawgS</a>"},{"pid":"3733f19a4106ba96a6bda0f346feefcd14461fb4","tid":1415963,"uid":262558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:22:17.000Z","msg":"罷工一定要說服到公共交通罷工。今日巴士無罷到。<br />\n草根階層真係只可以睇眼前既野。好難同佢講理念"},{"pid":"9b94fc4c8747a907cef5f59f0b5ccc721305a8de","tid":1415963,"uid":239250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:27:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6a14b9908e95691f249f02de8361d0218c97af3","tid":1415963,"uid":260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:31:14.000Z","msg":"&lt;&lt;&lt;核彈都唔割 齊齊幫手做文宣&gt;&gt;&gt;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1416562\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1416562</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}